{
  "chapter": "100",
  "title": "季布栾布列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "季布被购求得释",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人。以义气任侠闻名于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项籍（项羽）</span>让他率兵，屡次窘困<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">汉王（刘邦）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>灭亡后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高祖（刘邦）</span>悬赏<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>捉拿<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：季布\">布（季布）</span>，胆敢藏匿者，罪及三<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>藏匿在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">濮阳</span><span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">周氏</span>家。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">周氏</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>悬赏捉拿将军紧迫，追踪将至<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>家，将军若能听<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的话，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>敢献上一计；如果不能，情愿先自杀。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>答应了。于是剃去<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>的头发戴上项圈，穿上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">褐衣</span>，安置在<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">广柳车</span>中，连同他的家僮<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十人</span>，一起到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>地<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃家</span>处卖掉。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃家</span>心中知道这是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>，就买下来安置在田庄。告诫儿子说：\"田里的事听这奴隶的安排，务必和他同食。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃家</span>于是乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">轺车</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>，见<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汝阴侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">滕公</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">滕公</span>留<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃家</span>饮酒数日。因而对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">滕公</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>有什么大罪，皇上追捕这么急？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">滕公</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：季布\">布（季布）</span>多次替<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>困窘皇上，皇上怨恨他，所以一定要抓住他。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃家</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>看<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>是什么人？\" 回答：\"是贤者。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃家</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>子各为其主效力，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项籍（项羽）</span>效力，本是职责所在。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">项氏</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>子能都<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛杀</span>吗？<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今上</span>刚得<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，却因私怨追捕<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>，这怎能向<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>显示他的宽大！况且以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>的贤能，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>追捕得如此急迫，他不是北逃胡地就是南奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>罢了。忌恨<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">壮士</span>以资敌国，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">鞭</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚平王\">荆平王（楚平王）</span>之墓的缘由。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>何不从容地向皇上进言呢？\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">汝阴侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">滕公</span>心知<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃家</span>是大侠，猜测<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>就藏匿在他那里，便答应说：\"好。\" 等机会，果然依<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃家</span>所指的劝谏。皇上于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赦免</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>。当时，诸公都称赞<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>能摧折刚强化为柔顺，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃家</span>也因此名闻当世。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>被召见，谢罪，皇上<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">任命</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "谏阻伐匈奴",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉惠帝\">孝惠（汉惠帝）</span>时，为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中郎将</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>曾写信侮慢<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">吕后（吕雉）</span>，言辞不恭，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">吕后（吕雉）</span>大怒，召诸将商议。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樊哙</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>愿得<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十万众</span>，横行于<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>中。\" 诸将都顺从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕雉\">吕后（吕雉）</span>之意，说\"好\"。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">樊哙</span>可<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>！当年<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高帝（刘邦）</span>率兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四十馀万众</span>，尚被困于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平城</span>，如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">哙</span>怎能以<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十万众</span>横行<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>中，这是当面欺君！况且<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>因用兵于胡，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>等乘机起事。至今创伤未愈，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">哙</span>又当面阿谀，想动摇<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。\" 此时殿上众人都害怕，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>罢朝，于是不再议<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>之事。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "季布为河东守",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">河东守</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">孝文（汉文帝）</span>时，有人称赞他贤能，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">孝文（汉文帝）</span>召见，想任他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>。又有人说他勇猛，使<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>难以亲近。到了京师，在官邸留住一个月，被召见后又被遣回。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>便上前说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>无功而蒙宠，待罪于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河东</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>无故召<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>来，此人必是借<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>欺<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>；如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>到了，没得到任命就遣回，此人必又在诋毁<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>因<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>的赞誉而召<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，因<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>的诋毁而遣走<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>恐怕<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>有识之士听到后有以窥<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>的。\" 皇上默然惭愧，良久说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河东</span>是我的股肱郡，所以特意召<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：季布\">布（季布）</span>告辞返回任上。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "曹丘生扬布名",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹丘生</span>，是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">辩士</span>，屡次依势利招取<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金钱</span>。侍奉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贵人</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵同</span>等，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦长君</span>交好。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>听说后，寄信告诫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦长君</span>说：\"我听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹丘生</span>不是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>，不要和他来往。\" 等<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹丘生</span>归来，想取信求见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">窦长君</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：季布\">季（季布）</span>将军不喜欢您，您不要去。\" 他坚持求取介绍信，就前往了。派人先送去书信，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>果然大怒，等着<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹丘</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹丘</span>到了，便作揖对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人谚语说'得<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄金</span>百，不如得<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>一诺'，您怎样得到这声誉于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>之间呢？况且我是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人，您也是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>人。我为您宣扬名声于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，难道不是很重要吗？您怎么这样拒绝我呢！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>于是大为高兴，引他入内，留住数月，作为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上客</span>，厚礼送走。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>的名声之所以更加闻名，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹丘</span>宣扬的缘故。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "季心任侠",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季心</span>，气盖<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>，待人恭敬谨慎，为人任侠，方圆<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千里</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>都争着为他效死。他曾经<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>过人，逃亡到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>，藏匿在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁丝</span>处。对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁丝</span>以兄事之，像待弟一样对待<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">灌夫</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">籍福</span>等人。曾任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中司马</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郅都</span>也不敢不以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>相待。年轻人多次私自借用他的名义行事。当时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季心</span>以勇猛、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：季布\">布（季布）</span>以守诺，著称于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "丁公不忠被诛",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>的同母异父弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丁公</span>，任<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>将。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丁公</span>替<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>追击困迫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高祖（刘邦）</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>西，短兵相接，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高祖（刘邦）</span>危急，回头对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丁公</span>说：\"两位贤人难道要相互困斗吗！\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丁公</span>率兵而还，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">汉王（刘邦）</span>得以脱身。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>灭亡，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丁公</span>来谒见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高祖（刘邦）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘邦\">高祖（刘邦）</span>让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丁公</span>在军中示众，说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丁公</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>子不忠，使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>失去<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丁公</span>。\" 于是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丁公</span>，说：\"让后世做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人臣</span>的不要效法<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丁公</span>！\""
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "栾布早年",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栾布</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>人。当初<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">梁王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>为平民时，曾与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：栾布\">布（栾布）</span>交往。穷困时，在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>做佣工，为<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>家做帮工。数年后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>离去到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巨野</span>中为盗，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：栾布\">布（栾布）</span>被人掠卖，在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>做奴仆。他为主人家报仇，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧荼</span>提拔他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">都尉</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧荼</span>后来做了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕王</span>，以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：栾布\">布（栾布）</span>为将。等<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臧荼</span>反叛，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，俘获<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：栾布\">布（栾布）</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">梁王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>听说后，便向皇上进言，请求赎回<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：栾布\">布（栾布）</span>任<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">梁大夫</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "栾布哭彭越",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栾布</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，未回来，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>，以谋反罪责问，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">夷三族</span>。随即把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>头颅悬挂在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>城下，下诏说：\"有敢收葬吊唁者，立刻逮捕。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：栾布\">布（栾布）</span>从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>回来，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>头下奏事，祭奠并哭他。官吏抓了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：栾布\">布（栾布）</span>上报。皇上召见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：栾布\">布（栾布）</span>，骂道：\"你要与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>同反吗？我下令禁止人收葬，你偏祭奠哭他，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">越（彭越）</span>同反是明白的了。快把他烹了。\" 方要拖去烹刑，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：栾布\">布（栾布）</span>回头说：\"愿一言而死。\" 皇上说：\"什么话？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：栾布\">布（栾布）</span>说：\"当皇上被困于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>，战败于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>之间时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：项羽\">项王（项羽）</span>之所以不能西进，只因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">彭王（彭越）</span>据<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>地，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">合从</span>抗<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。当时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">彭王（彭越）</span>的态度一变，附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>则<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>败，附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>则<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>败。况且<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">垓下</span>之会战，没有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">彭王（彭越）</span>，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">项氏</span>就不灭。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>既定，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">彭王（彭越）</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">剖符</span>受封，也希望传诸万世。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>一次从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>征兵，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">彭王（彭越）</span>因病不去，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>就疑他谋反，反迹未现，就以苛小之罪<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">诛灭</span>他，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>恐怕<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span>人人自危。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">彭王（彭越）</span>已死，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>生不如死，请就烹吧。\" 于是皇上释放了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：栾布\">布（栾布）</span>的罪，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">任命</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">都尉</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "栾布晚年",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉文帝\">孝文（汉文帝）</span>时，任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕相</span>，升至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：栾布\">布（栾布）</span>于是声称：\"穷困不能自辱屈志，就不算人；富贵不能随心快意，就不算贤。\" 于是对曾经有恩于他的人厚厚报答，对有怨的人必以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>剪除。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>反叛时，以军功封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">俞侯</span>，再任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">燕相</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>之间都为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栾布</span>立社，称为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：栾布\">栾公（栾布）</span>社。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "栾贲失侯",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉景帝\">景帝（汉景帝）</span>中<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>去世。子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：栾贲\">贲（栾贲）</span>嗣位，任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太常</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">牺牲</span>不符合规定，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>的气概，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>以勇猛显名于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，亲身踏平敌军拔<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">旗</span>数次，可谓<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">壮士</span>。然而到被刑<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">戮</span>、为人奴却不自杀，何其卑下！他必自负其才能，所以受辱而不以为羞，想有所用而才能尚未施展，所以终成<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的名将。贤者确实看重自己的死。那些婢妾贱人因一时感慨而<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>者，并非真勇敢，是计谋已穷罢了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栾布</span>哭<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">彭越</span>，赴烹如归，他真知自己应何处之，不自重其死。即使是古时的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">烈士</span>，又怎能超过他！"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季布</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季心</span>，名声远播<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。 <span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">百金</span>一诺，十万军众都被拒。 出守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河东</span>，股肱之郡得人。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栾布</span>哭<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：彭越\">越（彭越）</span>，犯禁被俘。 赴<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鼎</span>非冤，真知所处。"
    }
  }
